Comment: 10,0:06:02.76,0:06:06.10,Default,,13,13,0,,We will now assign Samhain Festival duties to the teams.
Comment: 10,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Each team, please send one representative up to draw your lot.
