Comment: 10,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I have the worst luck in lotteries!
Comment: 10,0:06:14.61,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so do I...
Comment: 10,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You kids are in charge of fireworks!{## that thing doesn't look like it's about to knock up its sister and succumb to alcoholism at the age of 53}{that wasn't very nice}
Comment: 10,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks magic?!{## man why shouldn't this be specific?}{because I mistyped}
Comment: 10,0:06:22.95,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you...
Comment: 10,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Already taken, huh.
