Comment: 10,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning?!
Comment: 10,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the showpiece of the Festival!
Comment: 10,0:06:38.88,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. You maggots get cleaning duty.
Comment: 10,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning duty?
Comment: 10,0:06:43.43,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining teams should send their representatives at once!
Comment: 10,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to pick something.
