Comment: 10,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Comment: 10,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Representative of that team, get up here {\fax-0.2}now{\i0}.
Comment: 10,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucy! No, Lotte!
Comment: 10,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Comment: 10,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.41,Default,,525,0,0,,{\an1}Akko!
Comment: 10,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... this one?
Comment: 10,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got a bad feeling. Maybe...
Comment: 10,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose now, or I'll be choosing which of your nails to tear out! {ganbaruzoi}
Comment: 10,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine!
Comment: 10,0:07:10.87,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be the sacrifices.
Comment: 10,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifices?
Comment: 10,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of duty is that?
Comment: 10,0:07:19.67,0:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know what the sacrifices do?
Comment: 10,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This pot contains an age-old ghost,\N"Vajarois the Bewailing". {this name is 100% made up. it should probably be celticified}{## bah; also main reason for flipping the order was line length balance, true facts; also i hate when kinda mandatory diphthongs just don't exist in any variety of gaelic}
Comment: 10,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vajarois the Bewailing?
Comment: 10,0:07:29.02,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vajarois wakes with the midnight toll at the close of the Festival, wailing and flailing about.
Comment: 10,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That is when the sacrifices are offered.
Comment: 10,0:07:42.65,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After consuming them, Vajarois rests once more until the dawn of the next Samhain Festival.
Comment: 10,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The people on sacrifice duty die?!
Comment: 10,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no danger to your lives.
Comment: 10,0:07:52.09,0:07:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The sacrifices pass through the ghost's bowels and are safely excreted.
Comment: 10,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gross!
Comment: 10,0:07:58.18,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice duty! It's like poetry!{## pottery?}{pottery}
Comment: 10,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't pick a more fitting role for Akko if you tried!
Comment: 10,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Comment: 10,0:08:09.56,0:08:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We must focus on our Samhain Festival duties at hand. Save your prattle for later.
Comment: 10,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Comment: 10,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Diana Cavendish.
Comment: 10,0:08:20.16,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been voted in as Luna Nova's youngest ever Samhain Festival committee chair.
Comment: 10,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:08:31.54,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, rally around Diana and work together\Nto make this Samhain Festival a success.
Comment: 10,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 10,0:08:40.65,0:08:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the whole sacrifice duty?
Comment: 10,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the Samhain Festival supposed to be fun?
Comment: 10,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do they have to include this ghost eating sacrifices stuff?
Comment: 10,0:08:50.26,0:08:55.73,Default,,13,13,0,,"Vajarois the Bewailing was a member of the royal family of the Book Kingdom in the second century BCE. {I usually say BC but I guess it probably changed by now. also I can't find if the book kingdom is real}{## didn't find anything either}
Comment: 10,0:08:55.73,0:08:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She spent her life in happiness surrounded by friends.
Comment: 10,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, after she lost her friends in the last years of her life,{they're all gone by now}
Comment: 10,0:09:02.82,0:09:07.97,Default,,13,13,0,,Vajarois mourned, saying 'This world has nothing but sorrow', and eventually turned into a ghost of bewailing."
Comment: 10,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What, just because of that?
Comment: 10,0:09:11.08,0:09:16.32,Default,,13,13,0,,It goes on to say that since she's crying even in \Nher sleep, she needs to eat sacrifices to sate her hunger.{guess I'm assuming gender too?}{## male until proven otherwise}
Comment: 10,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Want one?
Comment: 10,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Vajarois!
Comment: 10,0:09:21.78,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault for crying all the time!
Comment: 10,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making {\fax-0.2}me{\i0} feel like crying here, geez!
Comment: 10,0:09:29.21,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All my hard work trying to be the Moonlit Witch\Nlike Chariot is going to go to waste.
Comment: 10,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Akko. Are you really trying to be chosen as the Moonlit Witch?
Comment: 10,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:09:37.23,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's going to happen. Diana will likely end up being selected.
Comment: 10,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Comment: 10,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Comment: 10,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes you so sure?
Comment: 10,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Diana comes from a prestigious family.
Comment: 10,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She was born with talent running through her veins. {the key point is talent, not wealth, so I couldn't use silver spoon}
Comment: 10,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you don't care about being the Moonlit Witch, Lotte?
Comment: 10,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here so that I can properly inherit my family's magic item shop.
Comment: 10,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Sucy?
Comment: 10,0:10:05.13,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought of passing through the inside of a ghost is giving me shivers! {in a good way. if it's unclear we chan change it}{## just made it a bit less of a reply to akko}
Comment: 10,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Comment: 10,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me.
Comment: 10,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Comment: 10,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Comment: 10,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean her.
Comment: 10,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one I can't believe, wanting to be the Moonlit Witch when you can't even ride a broom.
Comment: 10,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Comment: 10,0:10:23.34,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 10,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. Our duties fell to us randomly.{hidoi! they're all hidoi!}
Comment: 10,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your hopes up by putting your head in the clouds.
Comment: 10,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the perfect role for you?
Comment: 10,0:10:34.79,0:10:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we should prepare for our sacrifice duty meeting—
Comment: 10,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you all accept this?!
Comment: 10,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in charge of preparing the mirror for the Samhain Festival,
Comment: 10,0:10:51.99,0:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's something we need your advice about.
Comment: 10,0:10:55.01,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We collected all these mirrors, but we're not sure which one to use.
Comment: 10,0:10:59.15,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you pick the one you think is best?
Comment: 10,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. If these are our options...
Comment: 10,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this one contains the most magic power.
Comment: 10,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it appears to be a prankster.
Comment: 10,0:11:18.71,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Polishing it with fairy powder should rein in its mischievous spirit. {we used sprite before, but it's fairy powder. also not literal spirit}
Comment: 10,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 10,0:11:23.11,0:11:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll request the powder from the teachers.\NLet's go pick it up together.
Comment: 10,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:11:27.96,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're the committee chair!\NWe can always rely on you.
Comment: 10,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a shoe-in for Moonlit Witch!
Comment: 10,0:11:34.84,0:11:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But we cannot yet say for sure\Nwho will be selected as Moonlit Witch.
Comment: 10,0:11:39.56,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Comment: 10,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why am I hiding?
Comment: 10,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn thing.
Comment: 10,0:11:56.37,0:11:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest—you wish you were born with talent running through your veins.
Comment: 10,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like... {\fax-0.2}this{\i0}.
Comment: 10,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the?!
Comment: 10,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Diana?
Comment: 10,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Diana.
Comment: 10,0:12:09.92,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The program you submitted for the Samhain Festival is impressively thorough.
Comment: 10,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Comment: 10,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hold a meeting to discuss it.
Comment: 10,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! The pain!
Comment: 10,0:12:21.09,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach...
Comment: 10,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you unwell?
Comment: 10,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please—Please excuse me...
Comment: 10,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the pain...
Comment: 10,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Why? Why did this happen?!
Comment: 10,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a bit of a pinch.
Comment: 10,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't figure out how to read the summoning spell by ourselves.{## she sounds so different}
Comment: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one on this page.
Comment: 10,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, teach us!
Comment: 10,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Comment: 10,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Diana?
Comment: 10,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fine mess we are in.
Comment: 10,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you two have laid eyes on this spell...
Comment: 10,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are already under its curse.
Comment: 10,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse?!
Comment: 10,0:13:07.16,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing is done, you will become eighty-two years old within twenty-four hours!
Comment: 10,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-two...
Comment: 10,0:13:13.71,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...years old?
Comment: 10,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Comment: 10,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Place both of your hands atop your head.
Comment: 10,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Like this?
Comment: 10,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very good. Now then...
Comment: 10,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to write the curse-breaking spell!
Comment: 10,0:13:35.86,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Comment: 10,0:13:36.94,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stay like that until tomorrow morning, and the curse will be lifted.
Comment: 10,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't move until tomorrow morning?
Comment: 10,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Comment: 10,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, I have other business to attend to.
Comment: 10,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our savior!
Comment: 10,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Comment: 10,0:14:03.12,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Lady Diana. Please forgive me.
Comment: 10,0:14:06.22,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just completed my cleaning of your room.
Comment: 10,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Oh, Diana's room must be this way.
Comment: 10,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Diana.
Comment: 10,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you not returning to your room?
Comment: 10,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I was! I was just on my way there now.
Comment: 10,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Too close, too close!
Comment: 10,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}So this is where Diana and them live.
Comment: 10,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}But sneaking into someone else's room\Nis definitely crossing a line.
Comment: 10,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Diana.
Comment: 10,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to pass on a message for you.
Comment: 10,0:14:40.67,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was cleaning, your classmates\Ncame by in a rush, looking for you.{fuckin commas man. comma man}
Comment: 10,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see. Thank you for telling me.
Comment: 10,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Comment: 10,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Comment: 10,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a break... huh?
Comment: 10,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Whoa...
Comment: 10,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Diana's... diary?
Comment: 10,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop! I {\fax-0.2}definitely{\i0} can't look at this!
Comment: 10,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana?
Comment: 10,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?!
Comment: 10,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear her voice.
Comment: 10,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be back!
Comment: 10,0:15:17.46,0:15:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming in.
Comment: 10,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana.
Comment: 10,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We need your help.
Comment: 10,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can I be of service?
Comment: 10,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the Samhain Festival's Welcome Objet d'art. {I'm serious. apparently this refers to small objects, but I think it's tongue in cheek}
Comment: 10,0:15:32.74,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to get the statue of Great Witch Jennifer out here, but Professor told us to change her pose.
Comment: 10,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to use life-breathing magic\Non it, but it's too hard for us.
Comment: 10,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our only hope.
Comment: 10,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Leave all your hopes in these capable hands of mine! {Akko goes full Gion aka Kyoto Geisha here, for some reason I'm having trouble making it hammy}
Comment: 10,0:15:49.37,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There is not a thing that I cannot possibly do!
Comment: 10,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back, everyone!
Comment: 10,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I-I can make this work! I've been practicing metamorphosis magic every day!
Comment: 10,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Th-This is nothing.
Comment: 10,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ansolew Aroae! {she says it wrong}
Comment: 10,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ansolew Aroae! Ansolew Aroae!
Comment: 10,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Diana?
Comment: 10,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's having a bad day.
Comment: 10,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the wrong spell?
Comment: 10,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Comment: 10,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ansolew Airo!
Comment: 10,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko?!
Comment: 10,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? I'm back?
Comment: 10,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's a very good reason behind this...
Comment: 10,0:16:51.06,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the work of the mirror,\NI presume. It's easy to imagine.{## man, hikasa delivered a really good job. i guess she's a bit underrated, even considering she's semi-star tier}
Comment: 10,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:16:56.24,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I just had a meeting with Lotte and Sucy about your sacrifice duty.
Comment: 10,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really so irresponsible as to forget?
Comment: 10,0:17:04.94,0:17:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. I just can't get on board\Nwith being a sacrifice.
Comment: 10,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think that justifies your pointless prank?
Comment: 10,0:17:15.17,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever something doesn't go your way,\Nyou sulk and lose all motivation.
Comment: 10,0:17:19.93,0:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You play at being Chariot without the slightest knowledge of the history or tradition of magic.
Comment: 10,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to learn at this academy!
Comment: 10,0:17:26.26,0:17:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\fax-0.2}am{\i0} motivated! I'm serious about following in Chariot's footsteps!
Comment: 10,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious? You are?
Comment: 10,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it to you.
Comment: 10,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That my passion for magic is the real deal!
Comment: 10,0:17:41.10,0:17:45.47,Default,,0,0,40,,{\an8}Kagari Atsuko will be chosen as the Moonlit Witch during the Samhain Festival!
Comment: 10,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Comment: 10,0:17:48.56,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Comment: 10,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana sure is amazing.
Comment: 10,0:18:02.94,0:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}"This world was once abundant\Nwith the power of good magic.
Comment: 10,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}In our current era, however, magic is ever dwindling.
Comment: 10,0:18:10.75,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I plan to seek the ultimate power of the Grand Triskelion to revitalize magic once more." {we finally get more information. grand triskelion means "ultimate magic" in the kanji}{sorry, my symphogear is acting up}
Comment: 10,0:18:19.79,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And what am I, compared to her?!
Comment: 10,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you claimed that you'd become the Moonlit Witch in front of everyone.
Comment: 10,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ursula.
Comment: 10,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It just came out...
Comment: 10,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I have zero chance of winning...
Comment: 10,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero?
Comment: 10,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to admit it, but everyone's right.
Comment: 10,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana is amazing.
Comment: 10,0:18:44.18,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's more mature than I can even imagine being, and it's like she lives in a totally different world.
Comment: 10,0:18:50.18,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When I put myself next to her, all I see is a little kid.
Comment: 10,0:18:53.98,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, it's true that you have a tendency to leap before you look that you should consider fixing.
Comment: 10,0:19:02.90,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I bet that even Chariot failed and worried and got discouraged more than you'd expect.
Comment: 10,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What would Chariot do? {get this on a bracelet}
Comment: 10,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Dipper is so pretty.{## see, diana would've recognized chariot by now looking at this big fat hint, but akko is a bakko}
Comment: 10,0:19:19.12,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkling past the far edge of it is the North Star—Polaris.
Comment: 10,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ursula?
Comment: 10,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If Chariot was here, she might say something like this:
Comment: 10,0:19:33.44,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't compare yourself to others.\NDo what only you can do."
Comment: 10,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch over this for her.
Comment: 10,0:19:42.79,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Comment: 10,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Profes—
Comment: 10,0:19:46.73,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Comment: 10,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What only I can do...
Comment: 10,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This light...
Comment: 10,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Comment: 10,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like back then, it's the Fountain of Polaris.
Comment: 10,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what only I can do.
Comment: 10,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:20:59.91,0:21:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}This is from when someone was watching Chariot...
Comment: 10,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Chariot looks like she's having so much fun.
Comment: 10,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}H-Huh?
Comment: 10,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Chariot is so great.
Comment: 10,0:21:54.75,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Could it be that Chariot wasn't practicing to become the Moonlit Witch?
Comment: 10,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}It was more pure...
Comment: 10,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Arae Aryrha...
Comment: 10,0:22:06.62,0:22:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Huh? A spell?
Comment: 10,0:22:11.56,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff...
Comment: 10,0:22:17.11,0:22:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! This is what I can do!
Comment: 10,0:23:53.80,0:23:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Until tomorrow...
Comment: 10,0:23:54.94,0:23:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, right?
Comment: 10,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.67,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Goodness, what am I to do with you?
Comment: 10,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.47,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Laugh with me!
Comment: 10,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.41,Default - Alt,,0,525,0,,{\an3}Akko!
Comment: 10,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.47,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}You came!
Comment: 10,0:21:00.47,0:21:03.62,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}What happened? You're covered in dirt.
Comment: 10,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.67,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\an8\fax-0.2}What am I to do with you? {that's too much character}
Comment: 10,0:21:08.84,0:21:09.95,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Watch me!
Comment: 10,0:21:10.31,0:21:13.41,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}I can feel power in my heart when I say this chant!
Comment: 10,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.54,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Arae Aryrha! {arai ari-ra}
Comment: 10,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.99,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}I'm getting dizzy!
Comment: 10,0:21:27.69,0:21:29.65,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Geez... here.
Comment: 10,0:21:31.61,0:21:33.27,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Arae Aryrha!
Comment: 10,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.97,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Open your heart!
Comment: 10,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.47,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Let's laugh together!
Comment: 10,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.60,Default - Alt,,0,0,40,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Arae Aryrha!
